author: gscokart
msg: (IVY-586) don't stop the resolution if the module is relocated to an other version of the same module.  The complete fix requires to handle relocation in the resolution algorithm.  This version will continue the resolution taking partially into account the relocation, and printing an error.  Note that conflict resolution doesn't take into account the relocation
